long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sync your AliExpress orders with BeProfit

BeProfit is Shopify’s most accurate profit calculator. It provides an intuitive analytics dashboard to help you track and analyze all your business metrics, including profits and expenses, all in one place. The app presents your business data in easy-to-digest charts and graphs so you can really understand your store’s trends and optimize your bottom line.

With the click of a button, all your orders’ metrics will be automatically pulled into your BeProfit dashboard (as a single sum per order), including costs of shipping & handling, processing fees, taxes, COGS, profit and more.

There’s a lot more to BeProfit:

Discover your true business profits
Build, share and export custom reports or use predefined report templates
Easily integrate your advertising channels, including Facebook, Google, Snapchat, TikTok and more
Track your ads’ performance and gain valuable marketing insights
Make data-driven decisions to increase your profits

Learn more about BeProfit by visiting https://apps.shopify.com/beprofit-profit-tracker
